title: Marvel NOW! Week 52 11/13/2013
description:
It's been one year since the Marvel NOW! relaunch! What do you think about it so far?I didn't see a collected torrent for last this week's Marvel NOW! titles yet, so I thought I'd upload one. Included are:

All New X-Men 018
Avengers Arena 017
Captain America - Living Legend 03 (of 4)
Deadpool 019
Fearless Defenders 011
Savage Wolverine 011
Superior Spider-Man 021
The Superior Foes of Spider-Man 005 [this series is the tits]
Thor, God of Thunder 015
Wolverine 011
X-Men Gold 001

If you like them and have the money, buy them and support your favorite writers, artists, local comic shops and publishers. Thanks be to all the uploaders and scanners and seeders out there!
